<item>
            <title>[PIG-3073] POUserFunc creating log spam for large scripts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3073</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;POUserFunc got some new logging in the case where a JobConf isn&apos;t available. In certain cases (huge scripts with tons of UDFs), this is creating gigantic logs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12618650">PIG-3073</key>
            <summary>POUserFunc creating log spam for large scripts</summary>
